item.title: Safari 4 Beta
item.description: Safari 4 Beta is out and it is rocking. Apple has adopted (copied) quite a bit from Chrome interface and I have to say the browser looks and behaves awesomely under Windows 7. But, why bore you with senseless praise? Go download it, and see it for yourself.
